UIC Business Academic Departments
UIC Business is expanding and evolving to meet the needs of its students in an ever-changing global economy. Consistently ranked the number one undergraduate business school in Chicago, UIC Business is a destination for students who value a solid education with ready access to a vibrant business community. The college is redefining business education and building a stronger, more vibrant reputation. In addition to building a more robust curriculum and increased faculty selectivity, UIC Business is experiencing steady growth in its student population. UIC Business leaders and faculty have built dynamic departments, producing outstanding graduates who are sought after by the business community.








